Package com.example.eventapp.models

Class Event

java.lang.Object
com.example.eventapp.models.Event
All Implemented Interfaces:
HasDocumentId, Serializable
public class Event extends Object implements HasDocumentId, Serializable
Represents an Event in the application, containing details about the organizer, associated facility, event description, poster, schedule, and registration limits. Implements the HasDocumentId interface for Firestore integration.
